<div class="inner-page">

  <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f5f0e8 0%,#d8f3dc 100%);padding:90px 48px;text-align:center;">
    <div style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#2D6A4F;margin-bottom:14px;">Our Story</div>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(30px,4.5vw,52px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.1;margin:0 0 18px;">Born in Northern California.<br>Built for how you actually live.</h1>
      <p style="color:#6B6B6B;font-size:17px;line-height:1.65;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;">We didn't start a mushroom company. We started looking for something better — and when we couldn't find it, we built it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Origin story -->
  <section style="padding:80px 24px;background:#fff;">
    <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">The Origin</div>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,40px);font-weight:900;margin-bottom:28px;">Why Happie exists</h2>
      <div style="font-size:17px;color:#444;line-height:1.85;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;">
        <p>The energy drink market is a paradox. Products engineered to make you feel good — packed with synthetic stimulants, artificial colors, and enough sugar to spike your cortisol before your morning meeting even starts. We used them anyway, because the alternative was nothing.</p>
        <p>Meanwhile, functional mushrooms had decades of legitimate science behind them. Lion's Mane studied for cognitive support. Cordyceps used by Olympic athletes. Reishi prescribed in traditional medicine for immune balance and stress. All of it locked away in capsules that tasted like dirt and required remembering to take them.</p>
        <p>Happie Fungi Fusion started with a simple question: <strong>What if the thing you reached for tasted incredible and actually did something?</strong></p>
        <p>Two years of formulation. Dozens of flavor iterations. A commitment to fruiting body extracts, dual-extraction, and third-party testing on every batch. The result is a drink we're proud of — and one that's earned the trust of 50,000+ customers who've made it part of their daily routine.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section style="padding:80px 24px;background:var(--cream);">
    <div style="max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">What We Stand For</div>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:left;margin-bottom:40px;">Our commitments</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;">
        <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:20px;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07);">
          <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:16px;">🔬</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:10px;">Radical Transparency</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;">Every batch is third-party tested and QR-coded to the full lab report. You know exactly what's in your can — potency, purity, contaminants. No exceptions.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:20px;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07);">
          <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:16px;">🌱</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:10px;">Real Ingredients Only</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;">No artificial flavors, no synthetic vitamins, no shortcuts. Fruiting body mushroom extracts, organic agave, and natural flavors. The label says what it means.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:20px;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07);">
          <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:16px;">⚖️</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:10px;">Effective Doses</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;">2,000mg per can — formulated to match doses used in clinical research. Not trace amounts for label claims. Actual amounts that move the needle.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:20px;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07);">
          <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:16px;">🚫</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:10px;">No Alcohol. Ever.</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;">We built something you can drink at any time of day, in any setting, at any age. Clean energy that doesn't compromise your clarity or your character.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:20px;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07);">
          <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:16px;">🌍</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:10px;">Sustainable Sourcing</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;">Our mushrooms are cultivated — not wild-harvested — using sustainable agricultural practices. Ocean-derived minerals sourced responsibly. Packaging designed to minimize waste.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:20px;padding:32px;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07);">
          <div style="font-size:36px;margin-bottom:16px;">❤️</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:10px;">Community First</h3>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;">50,000+ customers. Real reviews. Real results. We read every piece of feedback and iterate constantly. Happie exists because of the people who believed in it early.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- By the numbers -->
